        <abstract>
            <p>Discusses the origin and advantages of sexual differentiation in terms of division of labour.</p>
            <p>Discusses the origin of the giraffe’s neck and the unsoundness of St G. J. Mivart’s view with respect to it.</p> 
<p>Points out an error in <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>.</p> 
        </abstract>
